WEBVTT

00:04:27.107 --> 00:04:30.462
Zaradi ljubosumja postanemo ljubiteljski pisatelji,

00:04:30.462 --> 00:04:32.478
kar je Proust dobro razumel.

00:04:32.478 --> 00:04:35.651
V prvem delu, V Swannovem svetu,

00:04:35.651 --> 00:04:37.475
ki je serija knjig,

00:04:37.475 --> 00:04:39.181
Swann, eden od glavnih junakov,

00:04:39.181 --> 00:04:42.409
ljubeče razmišlja o svoji ljubici

00:04:42.409 --> 00:04:44.101
in o tem, kako dobra je v postelji.

00:04:44.101 --> 00:04:47.143
Potem pa v nekaj povedih

00:04:47.143 --> 00:04:49.184
in to so Proustove povedi,

00:04:49.184 --> 00:04:50.696
torej so dolge kot reka,

00:04:50.696 --> 00:04:52.959
v nekaj povedih

00:04:52.959 --> 00:04:55.366
spremeni pogled in ugotovi:

00:04:55.366 --> 00:04:58.649
"Čakaj, vse, kar ljubim na tej ženski,

00:04:58.649 --> 00:05:02.420
bi lahko ljubil tudi kdo drug.